headline: Dollar Tree, Inc. to Host First Quarter Earnings Conference Call
summary: CHESAPEAKE, Va., May 21, 2025--Dollar Tree, Inc. (NASDAQ: DLTR), will report financial results for the first quarter 2025 ended May 3, 2025, before the stock market opens on Wednesday, June 4, 2025, followed by a conference call for investors and analysts at 8 a.m. EDT. Chief Executive Officer Mike Creedon and Chief Financial Officer Stewart Glendinning will discuss the company’s results and lead a question-and-answer session.
